Here you will be able to look at personal data in terms of progress, changes, variations and so on! Below you will find 3 categories of data visualisation:
Single value displays - looking at your current state;
Progress - where you will be able to see your current state on the way to your goal;
Timelines - looking at your progress through 3 different types of graphs.

The experiments will be split into 3 categories - LIGHT, CAFFEINE and SLEEP SCHEDULE. Each of them cover a different contextual factor that has a direct impact on your sleep hygiene.
 - Light looks at how either sunlight exposure and blue light impact your sleeping patterns;
 - Caffeine looks at how drugs impact your system when it comes to bedtime;
 - Sleep Schedule looks at how important a persistent schedule is towards a good seep.
